Program: Outlook
Title: Hiding the Children of Illegal Immigrants in France
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbs5l
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The French couple hiding the Russian child of illegal immigrants from the authorities. Also, Marta Cecchetto talks about her life as a model and girlfriend of World Cup footballer Luca Toni. An interview with crime writer Michael Connolly. A jailed Romanian victim of trafficing turned trafficer talks about the sex trafficing trade. Show less